description: Coelacanth Energy Inc. engages in the exploration, development, and production of oil and natural gas in Canada. It holds an average 95% working interest in approximately 151.5 net sections or 96,960 net acres of undeveloped Montney land in the Two Rivers area of northeastern British Columbia. The company was incorporated in 2022 and is headquartered in Calgary, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Robert John Zakresky C.A., CA
